{
  "stem": "19807.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was like a paramilitary in 1946, if you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But before that, I was also in a British detention camp because our-- we were in the underground and in the underground, as part of the underground, although I did not participate personally into that, but groups of our kibbutz went and they blew up some-- some bridges in protest of the British because the British had instituted a policy of stopping the refugees from the camps, the remnants of the Holocaust, to come to Israel.",
      "word_count": 76
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so in order for us to-- to show our total disagreement, that's what they did, whereby the more-- [SIGHS] --more ultra rights, the-- the [INAUDIBLE] and the [INAUDIBLE], they went into-- didn't stop even at killing soldiers.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I must tell you, there was a time in Israel where it was very, very close to jumping the fence and going over to them because I was enraged that our brothers could not come to Israel.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I stayed in the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in our group there were 42.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Off the top of my head, a couple of thousand maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm really not sure, but definitely in the hundreds, 1,800 to 2,000--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "More or less.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were-- they were dispersed all over the kibbutzim.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I have to tell you that the Bulgarian [INAUDIBLE] was one of the most industrious [INAUDIBLE] that came to Israel.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were self-sufficient, they were self-reliant, they immediately integrated into the mainstream.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a-- there was a wonderful group of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We don't have stars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We don't have a Victor Borge, we don't have a Spielberg that can really tell the whole world what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
